text: Daniel Norbe (born August 22, 1995) is a Swedish ice hockey defenceman. He is currently playing with Björklöven of the Hockeyallsvenskan (HA). Norbe made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with HV71 during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:HV71 players Category:Karlskrona HK players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen Category:Tingsryds AIF players Category:People from Växjö
